description:
In order to provide a dangerous combat training scenario for his men, Keroro steals Natsumi`s precious 623 autograph and tells her she has to infiltrate the secret base to retrieve it.  But are they really prepared for Natsumi at 62.3% over her normal combat strength?
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: L`infiltration de la base secrète / La femme la plus puissante de l`univers
Natsumi delves into the Secret Basement! / Hinata Aki, probably the Strongest Woman in Space
夏美 侵入! 秘密基地 であります / 日向秋 たぶん宇宙最強の女 であります
